---
title: Honeyed Duck Breast with Asian Fried Bok Choi and Mushroom, Jasmine Rice
description: Add a little bit of low-key luxury to your menu with our delicious honeyed duck breast recipe. To get the skin beautifully golden and crispy, we’ve pan-fried the duck first before finishing it off in the oven. Served on a bed of steamed rice, the duck’s sweet and sticky flavour works brilliantly with zesty stir-fried mushrooms and bok choy. The ultimate simple showstopper.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honeyed-duck-breast-15c82cee-d4c36001.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/honeyed-duck-breast-5b2cef2d30006c263c705e22-cdf1d76c.pdf
servings: 2
